# Formspree endpoint for the contact form.
# 1. Sign up at https://formspree.io/
# 2. Create a new form and copy its hashid (the part after /f/ in the URL).
# 3. Set the full endpoint here:
#
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/your-form-id

# For local dev, copy this file to .env.local and fill in your value.
# For GitHub Pages, set the same env var in the workflow before next build.
NEXT_PUBLIC_FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=
